# CNG / Prebuild — force EAS to regenerate the native folders from
# app.json on every build instead of reusing the committed snapshots.
# Without these entries, expo-doctor flags the project as a mixed-CNG
# state ("This project contains native project folders but also has
# native configuration properties in app.json"), and EAS silently
# skips syncing app.json plugin changes for the platform whose folder
# exists. The committed android/ stays as a local-dev cache for
# `npx expo run:android` only — EAS ignores it and prebuilds fresh.
# https://docs.expo.dev/workflow/prebuild/#usage-with-eas-build
/ios
/android
